1. In nodes VM, Run the getNodes.sh to get details of all started nodes into allNodes.job

	usage : sh getNodes.sh

2. Run the getsimnodes.sh to get details of specific type of nodes into selNodes.txt
	usage: sh getsimnodes.sh 6675 

3. Run the filterNodes.sh to filter the <NodeType> nodes from the allNodes.job into finalNodes.job.
	usage: sh filterNodes.sh allNodes.job selNodes.txt

4 Now ,from the stubs VM,  run the subscriber.sh on the nodes to activate the subscription before executing AVC burst.
	usage: sh subscriber.sh <NODES_FILE> <TIME_OUT> <LOGGING>
5 Then , run the trigger.sh to execute the AVC burst on the nodes.

6.The results will be stored in finalAll.job file.

